nodes.text: Morn was a Mon Calamari king of the Outer Rim planet Dac. Around 4500 BBY, the king became the first ruler of Dac to unite the Mon Calamari and Quarren people under the rule of a single monarchy.
Morn was mentioned in Strongholds of Resistance, a 2015 sourcebook of Fantasy Flight Games's Star Wars: Age of Rebellion roleplaying game.
